OL,3,CMan jailed for life for wife's murder
OL,4,Cafter car fire near Swansea hospital
OL,6,FA former electrician has been jailed
OL,7,Ffor life with a minimum term of 21
OL,8,Fyears after pleading guilty to killing
OL,9,Fhis wife with a hammer and then
OL,10,Fsetting her on fire.
OL,12,FSentencing David Clarke, Judge Paul
OL,13,FThomas said the 80-year-old caused
OL,14,FHelen "unimaginable pain and terror"
OL,15,Fdescribing this as an "especially
OL,16,Fsavage murder."
