OL,6,FPolice were called to Sketty Lane just
OL,7,Fafter 8.20 am on Friday, 22 September,
OL,8,Fby firefighters who were dealing with
OL,9,Fa burning black Honda Jazz car.
OL,11,FThe couple were subsequently taken to
OL,12,Fhospital with burns. Mrs Clarke
OL,13,Fsuffered multiple head injuries and
OL,14,Fsignificant burns to her body which
OL,15,Fled to her death two days later at
OL,16,FMorriston Hospital.
OL,18,FSentencing David Clarke, Judge Paul
OL,19,FThomas QC said: "You killed her
OL,20,F(Helen) in an utterly brutal and
OL,21,Fmerciless manner.
