OL,6,FHe added: "You have been an
OL,7,Faggressive, occasionally violent
OL,8,Fhusband for many years under a veneer
OL,9,Fof apparent respectability both in
OL,10,FAfrica and over latterly in this area.
OL,11,F"Despite your professed Christianity
OL,12,Fyour behaviour in private has never
OL,13,Fmatched your public image.J"Your
OL,14,Finfidelity with a woman in Africa had
OL,15,Fbeen concealed for around half a
OL,16,Fcentury until in the last year you
OL,17,Ftried to rekindle an old relationship.
OL,18,F"You went to the length of arranging a
OL,19,Fholiday to Australia with a hidden
OL,20,Fagenda of meeting up with a later with
OL,21,Fwhom you had been previously involved".
