OL,6,FJudge Thomas continued: "When she
OL,7,Fwanted nothing to do with you, in an
OL,8,Fact of spite you told your wife about
OL,9,Fthe affair at the airport on the way
OL,10,Fhome, leading of course to arguments
OL,11,Fbetween you thereafter."
OL,13,FThe couple's son, David Clarke Junior
OL,14,Fsaid: "We will never be able to
OL,15,Farticulate our devastation.
OL,17,F"Life as we know it has changed
OL,18,Fforever, they will never be as they
OL,19,Fwere before. The loss of our loving
OL,20,Fmother is insurmountable."
