OL,6,FHelen Clarke's family have issued a
OL,7,Ffull statement describing their mother
OL,8,Fas a "loving, kind and courageous
OL,9,Fwoman".
OL,11,FThey said: "We have endured
OL,12,Funimaginable pain since she was
OL,13,Fbrutally taken from us - and our
OL,14,Fchildren miss their Granny, who was
OL,15,Fextremely proud of them, so very much.
OL,17,F"We continue to do our utmost to
OL,18,Fsupport and protect them as we
OL,19,Fnavigate these very difficult
OL,20,Fcircumstances."
